{"pageProps":{"data":{"contentHtml":"<h4 id=\"bloonstd6-mod-helper\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\" class=\"position-relative\" href=\"#bloonstd6-mod-helper\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a><a href=\"README\" title=\"README\">BloonsTD6 Mod Helper</a></h4>\n<h3 id=\"btd_mod_helperapi\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\" class=\"position-relative\" href=\"#btd_mod_helperapi\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a><a href=\"README#BTD_Mod_Helper.Api\" title=\"BTD_Mod_Helper.Api\">BTD_Mod_Helper.Api</a></h3>\n<h2 id=\"ease-enum\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\" class=\"position-relative\" href=\"#ease-enum\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Ease Enum</h2>\n<p>Easing functions supported by <a href=\"BTD_Mod_Helper.Api.Tween\" title=\"BTD_Mod_Helper.Api.Tween\">Tween</a>.</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs language-csharp\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">enum</span> Ease\n</code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"fields\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\" class=\"position-relative\" href=\"#fields\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Fields</h3>\n<p><a name=\"BTD_Mod_Helper.Api.Ease.InCubic\"></a></p>\n<p><code class=\"hljs\">InCubic</code> 7</p>\n<p>Starts slowly and accelerates using a cubic curve.</p>\n<p><a name=\"BTD_Mod_Helper.Api.Ease.InOutCubic\"></a></p>\n<p><code class=\"hljs\">InOutCubic</code> 9</p>\n<p>Smooth cubic easing in both directions.</p>\n<p><a name=\"BTD_Mod_Helper.Api.Ease.InOutQuad\"></a></p>\n<p><code class=\"hljs\">InOutQuad</code> 6</p>\n<p>Smooth quadratic easing in both directions.</p>\n<p><a name=\"BTD_Mod_Helper.Api.Ease.InOutSine\"></a></p>\n<p><code class=\"hljs\">InOutSine</code> 3</p>\n<p>Smooth sine easing in both directions.</p>\n<p><a name=\"BTD_Mod_Helper.Api.Ease.InQuad\"></a></p>\n<p><code class=\"hljs\">InQuad</code> 4</p>\n<p>Starts slowly and accelerates using a quadratic curve.</p>\n<p><a name=\"BTD_Mod_Helper.Api.Ease.InSine\"></a></p>\n<p><code class=\"hljs\">InSine</code> 1</p>\n<p>Starts slowly and accelerates using a sine curve.</p>\n<p><a name=\"BTD_Mod_Helper.Api.Ease.Linear\"></a></p>\n<p><code class=\"hljs\">Linear</code> 0</p>\n<p>No easing.</p>\n<p><a name=\"BTD_Mod_Helper.Api.Ease.OutBack\"></a></p>\n<p><code class=\"hljs\">OutBack</code> 10</p>\n<p>Overshoots the destination before settling back.</p>\n<p><a name=\"BTD_Mod_Helper.Api.Ease.OutCubic\"></a></p>\n<p><code class=\"hljs\">OutCubic</code> 8</p>\n<p>Starts quickly and decelerates using a cubic curve.</p>\n<p><a name=\"BTD_Mod_Helper.Api.Ease.OutQuad\"></a></p>\n<p><code class=\"hljs\">OutQuad</code> 5</p>\n<p>Starts quickly and decelerates using a quadratic curve.</p>\n<p><a name=\"BTD_Mod_Helper.Api.Ease.OutSine\"></a></p>\n<p><code class=\"hljs\">OutSine</code> 2</p>\n<p>Starts quickly and decelerates using a sine curve.</p>","tableOfContentsHtml":"<nav class=\"toc\"><ol class=\"toc-level toc-level-1\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-item-h4\"><a class=\"toc-link toc-link-h4\" href=\"#bloonstd6-mod-helper\">BloonsTD6 Mod Helper</a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-item-h3\"><a class=\"toc-link toc-link-h3\" href=\"#btd_mod_helperapi\">BTD_Mod_Helper.Api</a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-item-h2\"><a class=\"toc-link toc-link-h2\" href=\"#ease-enum\">Ease Enum</a><ol class=\"toc-level toc-level-2\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-item-h3\"><a class=\"toc-link toc-link-h3\" href=\"#fields\">Fields</a></li></ol></li></ol></nav>","title":"BTD_Mod_Helper.Api.Ease"}},"__N_SSG":true}